-- p1-parallel-confluence.cell — frame 4 (final)
-- Ready set: { combine } — all three inputs now bound
-- combine is ⊢= (deterministic) — no LLM call needed

⊢= combine
  given poet→poem ≡ "Silver disc above\nPulling tides across the dark\nOld companion, still"
  given scientist→fact ≡ "The Moon is slowly drifting away from Earth at about 3.8 centimeters per year, meaning it was much closer and appeared far larger in the sky billions of years ago."
  given child→question ≡ "If the moon is made of rock, why does it glow at night?"
  yield document

  ⊢= document ← "POEM:\n" + poet→poem + "\n\nFACT:\n" + scientist→fact + "\n\nQUESTION:\n" + child→question

  yield document ≡ "POEM:\nSilver disc above\nPulling tides across the dark\nOld companion, still\n\nFACT:\nThe Moon is slowly drifting away from Earth at about 3.8 centimeters per year, meaning it was much closer and appeared far larger in the sky billions of years ago.\n\nQUESTION:\nIf the moon is made of rock, why does it glow at night?"

-- oracle checks:
--   ⊨ document contains all three inputs → ✓

-- COMPLETE: all cells frozen. 5 cells, 4 eval-one steps.
-- (config was trivial — 1 step. poet/scientist/child — 3 parallel steps.
--  combine — 1 deterministic step.)

-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- OBSERVATIONS (as Cell — not markdown)
-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

⊢ obs-confluence
  given §p1-parallel-confluence
  yield observations

  ⊢= observations ← "CONFLUENCE: poet, scientist, child were all ready after frame 0. I executed them poet→scientist→child but any order works. The program has 3! = 6 valid execution orderings for frames 1-3. Confluence guarantees same final document."

⊢ obs-pass-through
  given §p1-parallel-confluence
  yield observations

  ⊢= observations ← "DESIGN SMELL: config is a pass-through cell. It takes a given with ≡ and yields the same value. This is boilerplate. The spec should support top-level bindings: 'given topic ≡ the moon' at program scope, without wrapping in a cell. Config cells that just relay constants are ceremony, not computation."

⊢ obs-deterministic
  given §p1-parallel-confluence
  yield observations

  ⊢= observations ← "COMBINE IS CLEAN: ⊢= combine works perfectly. String concatenation on frozen values is pure classical computation. No LLM call, no oracle ambiguity. This is crystallization done right — the cell was born deterministic. The 3 soft cells (poet, scientist, child) could potentially crystallize too, but only after enough data to extract templates (see distillation-loop)."

⊢ obs-oracle-trivial
  given §p1-parallel-confluence
  yield observations

  ⊢= observations ← "ORACLE TRIVIALITY: the oracle on config (topic is a noun phrase) is tautological — we put the value there. Same pattern from R13. Oracles on givens with ≡ are assertions about the programmer, not the computation. They should be parse-time checks, not runtime oracles."
